msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.45:0.2"
msgid "5. Sagāthakapuññābhisandavagga "
msgstr "5. Overflowing Merit, With Verses "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 45. Dutiyamahaddhanasutta → dutiyaaḍḍhasuttaṃ (bj) | mahaddhana or aḍḍha 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn55.45:0.3"
msgid "45. Dutiyamahaddhanasutta "
msgstr "45. Rich (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn55.45:1.1"
msgid "“Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako ‘aḍḍho mahaddhano mahābhogo mahāyaso’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a noble disciple who has four things is said to be rich, affluent, wealthy, and famous. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn55.45:2.1"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn55.45:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha … "

msgctxt "sn55.45:2.3"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn55.45:2.4"
msgid "Dhamme … pe … "
msgstr "the teaching … "

msgctxt "sn55.45:2.5"
msgid "saṅghe … pe … "
msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

msgctxt "sn55.45:2.6"
msgid "ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi. "
msgstr "And they have the ethical conduct loved by the noble ones … leading to immersion. "

msgctxt "sn55.45:2.7"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako ‘aḍḍho mahaddhano mahābhogo mahāyaso’ti vuccatī”ti. "
msgstr "A noble disciple who has these four things is said to be rich, affluent, wealthy, and famous.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.45:2.8"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

